snippet.description:

The Aussie bowling attack stepped up on day four of the test match. Pat Cummins and Nathan Lyon picked up four wickets each and gave England's batters a hard time. England however managed to score 273 runs in the 66.2 overs they played. Australia then played 30 overs before the end of day four and scored 107 runs, but lost 3 big wickets in the process. England needs 7 wickets whereas Australia needs 174 runs on the final day to win the first test match.

snippet.description:
Aaditya Pandey has brought AIR-48 to the UPSC examination 2023 and will become IAS. Once people used to tell their father that their son will not be able to do anything and he also failed in 10th class. Then somehow he did engineering and then did MBA. Then he had a breakup, after which he decided that he would crack UPSC. After working hard for 3 years and failing twice in UPSC, he cracked UPSC and got AIR-48. snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3801: Leave Ki Permission
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide struggles to pen down the "Thought of the Day," or Suvichaar, on the Gokuldham Society Board, so Jetha offers his help. Bhide refuses to take anybody's help, and he writes down the Suvichaar in reference to the environmental nurturing done by Tapu Sena. Jetha decides to accompany Taarak to work, but he flees when Anjali offers him her diet food. Later, Taarak gets surprised when he sees that today Anjali has prepared delicious food instead of bland diet food. Anjali states that the reason for such preparation is that today is their first meeting anniversary, and she requests that Taarak take a leave from his work. Will Taarak's boss grant him a day off?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay‚Äôs advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.description:

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 14 Teaser - 19th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay‚Äôs advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: Tiku Weds Sheru - Official Trailer | Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Avneet Kaur | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video Presents
Tiku Weds Sheru Official Trailer
Directed by Sai Kabir
Starring Nawazuddin Siddiqui and Avneet Kaur
Produced by Kangana Ranaut

Official Release Date June 23, 2023 on Prime Video 

About:
Sheru and Tiku are marginalized souls from the underprivileged strata of society. They are ambitious for a better life but, life has different plans for them. Shiraz, popularly known as Sheru, hails from Bhopal, a small-town in India. Sheru comes to Mumbai in search of a better life. Being semi-literate, he works as a pimp for a local don, Shahid Bhai, and also as a junior artist as a decoy job, where he finds girls for his pimping business. He risks everything to win the confidence of his boss to be promoted as an equal partner. Taslim, aka Tiku, lives with her large conservative Muslim family in Bhopal. To break free from her family, she runs away to Delhi under the pretext of higher studies, where she falls in love with a man from a different religion, but her family marry her off to the first available eligible bachelor, Sheru. Sheru accepts the proposal in desperation of repaying a loan, while Tiku sees Sheru as her passport to freedom. However, Sheru falls in love with Tiku but they get caught between the chaos of the underworld, drugs, and romance and face one tragedy after the other without any time to deal with their sorrow.

Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video‚Äôs exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ‚Çπ599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. *About* 
------------

           Yeh kahani hai ek sidhi sadhi, padhi likhi, pyaari si, Pratigya aur ameer, bigdel, badtameez Krishna ki. Pratigya ki parvarish hui ek sadharan par acche parivaar mein jaha padhai aur sanskaron ko diya gaya bohot mahatva. Wahi doosri taraf apne parivaar mein Krishna ne dekhi zulm aur paise ki taakat. Isi taakat ke dum par zabardasti ki Krishna ne Pratigya se shaadi. 
           Pratigya ke sasural aur maayke mein hai zameen aur aasmaan ka faasla. Krishna ki haveli mein prem aur aadar ka hai akaal. Aise mein kya hoga Pratigya ka haal? Waqt ke sath Pratigya- Krishna ne kiya hazaaron mushkilon ka saamna aur door hua dono ke beech ka faasla. Ek anchaha rishta ban gaya sacche pyaar ki misaal.

localized.description:
VYRL Originals is now ready to unveil their new single to welcome the rains in 2023. After the massive triple successes of Baarish (2020) Baarish Ban Jaana (2021) and Baarish Aayi Hai in 2022, we now give you "Barsaat Aa Gayi". 

Composed by the talented composer duo Javed Mohsin, written by wordsmith Kunal Vermaa and sung in the stunning voices of Shreya Ghoshal and Stebin Ben . Barsaat Aa Gayi also reunites the superhit on-screen pair of Hina Khan and Shaheer Sheikh, from their previous successful collaboration of Baarish Ban Jaana. 

Get ready for the monsoon song of 2023 - Barsaat Aa Gayi
